<li><a href="http://www.untitledtheater.com/havel/essays-multimedia/letter-to-bush.html" class="external text" title="http://www.untitledtheater.com/havel/essays-multimedia/letter-to-bush.html" rel="nofollow">An Open Letter to George Bush</a> partly on this issue</li>
